        "solution_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">(ক) চাকরির প্রথম দিনেই এমন ধাক্কা </span><span class=\"english\">খাওয়া</span><span class=\"english\"> কোনো ভালো কথা নয়। - বাধা </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(খ) চাকরি খুঁজতে খুঁজতে </span><span class=\"english\">সারা</span><span class=\"english\"> হলাম, তবুও চাকরি মিললো না। - হতাশ </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(গ) জীবনে সফল হতে চাইলে </span><span class=\"english\">মাটি</span><span class=\"english\"> কামড়ে পড়ে থাকতে হবে। - নাছোড়বান্দা </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(ঘ) কথাটা পাঁচ </span><span class=\"english\">কান</span><span class=\"english\"> করো না। - প্রকাশ </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(ঙ) </span><span class=\"english\">বড়ো</span><span class=\"english\"> যদি হতে চাও, </span><span class=\"english\">ছোটো</span><span class=\"english\"> হও তবে। - বি</span><span class=\"english\">নীত</span><span> </span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বণ্টন</span><span class=\"english\">:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">প্রতিটি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বা</span><span class=\"english\">ক্যে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দগুলো কোন অর্থে বসেছে তা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সঠিকভাবে</span><span class=\"english\"> নির্ণয় ক</span><span class=\"english\">রার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">১</span><span class=\"english\">×</span><span class=\"english\">৫= ০৫ নম্বর।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">সমার্থক শব্দ বা খুব কাছাকাছি অর্থ লিখতে পারলে নম্বর দিয়ে দেব। তবে মূল অর্থকে প্রতিফলিত করে না এমন অর্থ নিব না।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">বি.দ্র. বানান ভুল করলে </span><span class=\"english\">কোনো </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর পাবে না।</span></p><p></p>"
    },
    {
        "question_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">Write a paragraph on </span><span class=\"english\">‘Goals and Expectations for Your University Education’ </span><span class=\"english\">within 10 sentences</span><span class=\"english\">.</span><span class=\"english\">      10</span></p>",
        "options_html": [],
        "correct_answer_html": null,
        "solution_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">                                           Goals and Expectations for My University Education.</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">My goals for university education are to deepen my expertise in a chosen discipline while gaining a well-rounded understanding of other fields. I seek to develop analytical thinking, research skills and a global perspective that will prepare me for professional and personal challenges. I aim to engage in collaborative projects, internships, and extracurricular activities to enhance both academic knowledge and practical experience. I expect the university to provide access to quality resources, diverse perspectives and a supportive learning environment that fosters intellectual growth. Furthermore, I hope to build meaningful relationships with professors and peers, contributing to a network that will last beyond my academic years. My education </span><span class=\"english\">should challenge me to think critically, question assumptions and innovate within my field. I also expect it to cultivate essential life skills such as time management, resilience and adaptability. Ultimately, I want my university education to serve as a foundation for a fulfilling career, continuous learning and personal development</span><span class=\"english\">.</span><span> </span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">Marks Distribution:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">Highest Marks ----------------------------------------------------------------09 Marks</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(A) For Title (</span><span class=\"english\">Goals and Expectations for My University Education.)</span><span class=\"english\"> --------------------------</span><span class=\"english\">01</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">Mark</span><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(B)</span><span class=\"english\"> Topic Sentence (Introduction)</span><span class=\"english\"> ------------------------------------</span><span class=\"english\">01 Mark</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">The user aims to deepen their expertise in a specific university discipline while also acquiring a broad understanding of other academic areas.</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(C) Context Explanation </span><span class=\"english\">---------------------------------------------------------</span><span class=\"english\">06 Marks</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">• Develop analytical thinking, research skills, and a global perspective for future challenges.</span><span class=\"english\"><br/>‎• Engage in collaborative projects, internships, and extracurricular activities to gain practical experience.</span><span class=\"english\"><br/>‎• Access quality resources, diverse perspectives, and a supportive learning environment for intellectual growth.</span><span class=\"english\"><br/>‎• Build lasting relationships with professors and peers.</span><span class=\"english\"><br/>‎• Be challenged to think critically, question assumptions, and innovate.</span><span class=\"english\"><br/>‎• Cultivate essential life skills like time management, resilience, and adaptability.</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(D) Conclusion ---------------------------------------------------------------------------01 Mark</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">The user's university education is intended to establish a basis for a fulfilling career, ongoing learning, and personal advancement.</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">Instructions:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">1. </span><span class=\"english\">For every 3 spelling/grammatical mistakes, 01 mark has to be deducted.</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">2</span><span class=\"english\">. We will consider up to 12 sentences. However, if a student writes more than 12 sentences but less than double (20 sentences), 50% of the deserving marks must be deducted. If it becomes double (20 sentences), full marks have to be deducted. </span><span class=\"english\">Comment: Write within 10 sentences.</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">3. </span><span class=\"english\">Students must write within a para. If a student writes more than one para, half of the deserving marks must be deducted. </span><span class=\"english\">(Comment: Write within single/one para)</span><span class=\"english\">.</span><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">4.</span><span class=\"english\"> For writing only the title of the paragraph bears no mark.</span></p>"
    },
    {
        "question_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">Translate the following paragraph into English:</span><span> </span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span class=\"english\">5</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">শিক্ষা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রথমত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিষয়টি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সেটা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হলো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নিজেদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিষয়ে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আমাদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সতর্ক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আমাদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যক্তিত্বের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">উন্নয়ন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঘটায়</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">যখন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আমরা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিদ্যালয়ে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যাই</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">আমরা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সেই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ক্লাসের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অংশ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হওয়ার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">এবং</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বন্ধুত্বের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রয়োজনীয়তা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অনুভব</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করি</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">তারপর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আমরা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আমাদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নিজস্ব</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">চিন্তায়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ব্যাপক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পরিসরে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিদ্যালয়কে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অন্তর্ভুক্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">এবং</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অবশেষে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আমাদের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দেশকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অন্তর্ভুক্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করি</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">এভাবে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শিক্ষা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রত্যেক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শিশুকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সমাজের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">একজন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সক্রিয়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সদস্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">এবং</span><span class=\"english\"> এর </span><span class=\"english\">কল্যাণে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কাজ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তৈরি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">থাকে</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p>",
        "options_html": [],
        "correct_answer_html": null,
        "solution_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">Translation:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">The first thing education does is to give us an awareness about ourselves which leads to the development of our personality. As we begin school, we feel the need to belong to the class and make friends. We then expand our sense of belonging to include the school at large and finally country. Education thus prepares every child to become an active member of the community and work for its welfare.</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">Instructions:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">* For accurate translation using correct grammar, punctuation, and sentence structure students will get full marks. For writing each sentence correctly 01 mark but for the 3</span><span class=\"english\"><sup>rd</sup></span><span class=\"english\"> sentence 02 marks.</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">* For every 03 grammatical/spelling errors 01 mark has to be deducted.</span></p>"
